    <item>
      <title>意大利批准国有银行行长连任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/italy-grants-new-term-for-state-lender-chief-after-quotas-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[达里奥·斯坎纳皮科 (Dario Scannapieco) 被任命出任意大利最高职位之一，五名女性被任命为国有银行 Cassa Depositi e Prestiti SpA 的董事会成员，结束了因女性职位而引发的争吵，此前该争吵令意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 的政府感到尴尬。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/italy-grants-new-term-for-state-lender-chief-after-quotas-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 16:40:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍勃·梅内德斯陪审团询问法官是否需要一致同意才能宣判无罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/bob-menendez-jury-asks-judge-whether-unanimity-needed-to-acquit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，美国参议员鲍勃·梅嫩德斯腐败案的陪审员询问法官，是否必须一致同意才能对任何罪名作出无罪宣判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/bob-menendez-jury-asks-judge-whether-unanimity-needed-to-acquit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 16:20:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普上台威胁州和地方政府减税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-s-rise-threatens-tax-break-for-state-and-local-governments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普竞选第二任总统的势头再次引发了人们的担忧，即长期以来的市政债券税收减免可能会被取消，以帮助支付永久性减税的费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-s-rise-threatens-tax-break-for-state-and-local-governments</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 16:15:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
